  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Long-term follow-up of a randomized clinical trial of Lichtenstein's operation versus mesh
      plug for inguinal hernia repair based on the following published study &quot;Randomized clinical
      trial of Lichtenstein's operation versus mesh plug for inguinal hernia repair. Br J Surg.
      2007 Jan;94(1):36-41.&quot;

      Primary endpoints is recurrence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
